Exercise 1.4 Represent the following in Prolog:
1. Butch is a killer.
    killer(butch).
2. Mia and Marcellus are married.
    married(mia, marcellus).
3. Zed is dead.
    dead(zed).
4. Marcellus kills everyone who gives Mia a footmassage.
    kills(marcellus, X) :- footmassage(mia, X).
5. Mia loves everyone who is a good dancer.
    loves(mia, X) :- good_dancer(X).
6. Jules eats anything that is nutritious or tasty.
    doesnt_eat(jules, X) :- nutritious(X).    Err: eats instead of doesnt_eat
    doesnt_eat(jules,X) :- tasty(X).          Text comprehension error.


